msgctxt "72_Katsuragi"
msgid "All right, let's get down to business."
msgstr "...Bien, entonces, pasemos al tema principal."

msgctxt "84_Katsuragi"
msgid "Tanimura-san. You said you wanted to know\\r\n"
"the truth about what happened to your father."
msgstr "Tanimura-san, dijiste que querías saber la verdad\\r\n"
"sobre la muerte de tu padre, ¿no?"

msgctxt "96_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah... About how he was murdered."
msgstr "Sí... Sobre cómo fue asesinado."

msgctxt "108_Tanimura"
msgid "It had something to do with the attempt on\\r\n"
"Yoshiharu Ueno's life 25 years ago, right?"
msgstr "¿No estará relacionado con el ataque a Yoshikazu\\r\n"
"Ueno de hace 25 años?"

msgctxt "120_Katsuragi"
msgid "I'm not one to beat around the bush,\\r\n"
"so I'll just say it. You're mistaken."
msgstr "No soy de andar con rodeos, así que lo\\r\n"
"diré claramente. ...Estás equivocado."

msgctxt "156_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh really? Heh, maybe you didn't know,\\r\n"
"but I was there when Arai killed Shibata."
msgstr "¿Qué me estás diciendo? ¿Que no es cierto?\\r\n"
"...Yo estuve presente cuando Arai mató a Shibata."

msgctxt "168_Tanimura"
msgid "Your trigger man said it himself,\\r\n"
"that you and Shibata were connected."
msgstr "Sé que tú y Shibata estaban conectados\\r\n"
"con el caso de hace veinticinco años."

msgctxt "180_Tanimura"
msgid "My dad risked his life to find out\\r\n"
"that connection on his own."
msgstr "...Mi padre se dio cuenta de que ese incidente\\r\n"
"fue algo que tú y Shibata planearon..."

msgctxt "192_Tanimura"
msgid "And that's what got him killed. Isn't it?"
msgstr "Y se supone que lo mataron debido a eso, ¿no?"

msgctxt "204_Katsuragi"
msgid "There is some truth to that, Tanimura-san..."
msgstr "Hay algo de verdad en eso, Tanimura-san..."

msgctxt "216_Katsuragi"
msgid "Namely, that your father did his homework\\r\n"
"on Shibata and I regarding the past incident."
msgstr "Tu padre descubrió que Shibata y yo estábamos\\r\n"
"involucrados en aquel incidente."

msgctxt "228_Katsuragi"
msgid "In fact, the two of us authored that script."
msgstr "Shibata y yo fuimos los autores de aquel incidente de hace veinticinco años."

msgctxt "240_Katsuragi"
msgid "So I knew the exact time and place\\r\n"
"Taiga Saejima would fulfill his duty."
msgstr "...Yo sabía que ese día, a esa hora,\\r\n"
"Taiga Saejima vendría solo a realizar el ataque."

msgctxt "252_Tanimura"
msgid "Hold up. You're telling me you planned on\\r\n"
"being a victim... of a shooting you set up?"
msgstr "Espera un momento... ¿No fuiste tú una de\\r\n"
"las víctimas en aquel incidente?"

msgctxt "264_Tanimura"
msgid "How did you think you'd survive?"
msgstr "¿Cómo lograste sobrevivir?"

msgctxt "276_Katsuragi"
msgid "Didn't I just tell you?"
msgstr "Je... Ya lo sabía, ¿no te lo acabo de decir?"

msgctxt "288_Katsuragi"
msgid "I knew every last detail of how\\r\n"
"Saejima would attack in advance."
msgstr "...Yo estaba al tanto de cómo\\r\n"
"Saejima llevaría a cabo el ataque."

msgctxt "300_Tanimura"
msgid "You wore body armor?"
msgstr "¿Llevabas un chaleco antibalas?"

msgctxt "312_Katsuragi"
msgid "Something like that. Let's just say I was\\r\n"
"thorough with my preparations. That's all."
msgstr "Más o menos. Me preparé con anticipación,\\r\n"
"por eso pude sobrevivir. Eso es todo."

msgctxt "348_Tanimura"
msgid "So, you conspired with Shibata to eliminate your\\r\n"
"family's officers and make it look like a Tojo hit."
msgstr "Así que tú y Shibata conspiraron para asesinar a los oficiales\\r\n"
"de tu familia, haciéndolo parecer un ataque del Tojo."

msgctxt "360_Tanimura"
msgid "And you did this knowing you could end up dead?"
msgstr "A pesar de la posibilidad de que murieras tú también."

msgctxt "372_Katsuragi"
msgid "At the time, I was only 22.\\r\n"
"Shibata himself was 30."
msgstr "En ese entonces, yo tenía 22 años\\r\n"
"y Shibata, 30."

msgctxt "384_Katsuragi"
msgid "Both of us understood that rising up the ranks at\\r\n"
"our age meant decisive action had to be taken."
msgstr "Los dos sabíamos que para ascender en la organización\\r\n"
"a nuestra edad era necesario actuar con decisión."

msgctxt "396_Tanimura"
msgid "You did become a lieutenant in the Ueno Seiwa.\\r\n"
"And Shibata rose to the top of the Tojo."
msgstr "Lograste convertirte en teniente en el Ueno Seiwa.\\r\n"
"Y Shibata llegó a lo más alto del Tojo."

msgctxt "408_Tanimura"
msgid "I'd say your plan was a success."
msgstr "Yo diría que su plan fue un éxito."

msgctxt "420_Katsuragi"
msgid "That would be an accurate conclusion."
msgstr "Supongo que sí."

msgctxt "432_Tanimura"
msgid "You seem rather nonchalant about all this."
msgstr "...¿Por qué lo dices con tanta ligereza?"

msgctxt "444_Katsuragi"
msgid "Well, it has been 25 years."
msgstr "Bueno, ya han pasado 25 años desde eso."

msgctxt "456_Katsuragi"
msgid "I could give you a play-by-play down to the\\r\n"
"minute, and the police still couldn't touch me."
msgstr "...incluso si la policía se entera de\\r\n"
"esto, no tengo nada que temer."

msgctxt "468_Tanimura"
msgid "True, the statute of limitations would apply...\\r\n"
"As long as you kept your hands clean."
msgstr "Es cierto, la ley de prescripción aplicaría...\\r\n"
"pero en la yakuza eso no existe."

msgctxt "480_Tanimura"
msgid "That's why you used Yasuko-san to eliminate\\r\n"
"Shibata's men, and Arai to wipe out their boss."
msgstr "Por eso manipulaste a Yasuko para que eliminara a los hombres\\r\n"
"de Shibata y luego ordenaste a Arai que matara a Shibata."

msgctxt "492_Tanimura"
msgid "Sound about right?"
msgstr "Así que eso es lo que pasó..."

msgctxt "504_Katsuragi"
msgid "Yes, I suppose it does."
msgstr "Pues sí, supongo."

msgctxt "516_Tanimura"
msgid "Though I doubt you'd admit your involvement\\r\n"
"in court... Fine, let's get back on track."
msgstr "¿Vas a seguir insistiendo en que no fuiste tú el autor intelectual?\\r\n"
"...Bueno, no importa. Volvamos al tema."

msgctxt "528_Tanimura"
msgid "Why did my father have to die 25 years ago?\\r\n"
"I want a real answer."
msgstr "¿Por qué era necesario que mi padre muriera hace 25 años?\\r\n"
"Quiero una respuesta real."

msgctxt "540_Katsuragi"
msgid "Your father, the Tanimura-san of my generation,\\r\n"
"had discovered Shibata and I were behind the hit."
msgstr "Tu padre... el Tanimura-san de mi generación, había\\r\n"
"descubierto que Shibata y yo estábamos detrás del ataque."

msgctxt "552_Katsuragi"
msgid "But he stumbled onto something even bigger\\r\n"
"during his investigation."
msgstr "Pero en el proceso de esa investigación, descubrió\\r\n"
"algo aún más grande."

msgctxt "564_Tanimura"
msgid "And what exactly was that?"
msgstr "¿Y qué fue lo que descubrió?"

msgctxt "576_Katsuragi"
msgid "Corruption."
msgstr "...Corrupción."

msgctxt "588_Katsuragi"
msgid "Digging in deeper led him to uncover corruption\\r\n"
"within the upper echelons of the police force."
msgstr "...Tu padre, mientras investigaba el caso, descubrió\\r\n"
"la corrupción dentro de la policía."

msgctxt "600_Tanimura"
msgid "Corruption... in the force?"
msgstr "¿Corrupción... en la policía?"

msgctxt "624_Katsuragi"
msgid "You may not know this, but the police\\r\n"
"staged a cover-up of the hit."
msgstr "...Puede que esto te sorprenda, pero\\r\n"
"la policía encubrió el ataque."

msgctxt "636_Katsuragi"
msgid "They concealed the real killer,\\r\n"
"and Taiga Saejima took the fall."
msgstr "...Para ocultar al verdadero asesino\\r\n"
"del caso, que no es Saejima Taiga."

msgctxt "648_Tanimura"
msgid "What do you mean by \"real\" killer?"
msgstr "¿El \"verdadero\" asesino... dices?"

msgctxt "660_Katsuragi"
msgid "Just what I said. Saejima popped our boys with\\r\n"
"bullets, but someone else finished the job."
msgstr "Así es... Taiga Saejima atacó a nuestros hombres,\\r\n"
"pero alguien más fue quien los remató."

msgctxt "672_Tanimura"
msgid "Yasuko-san did mention another\\r\n"
"perpetrator... So you weren't lying."
msgstr "Yasuko-san mencionó a otro perpetrador...\\r\n"
"Así que no estabas mintiendo."

msgctxt "684_Katsuragi"
msgid "Your old man figured it out pretty quick."
msgstr "Tu padre descubrió la identidad del verdadero asesino y..."

msgctxt "696_Katsuragi"
msgid "What he didn't bargain for was an institution\\r\n"
"that would purposely bury his work..."
msgstr "Al investigar el caso, descubrió tanto al verdadero\\r\n"
"asesino como la corrupción policial que lo encubrió..."

msgctxt "708_Katsuragi"
msgid "...Let alone bury him along with it."
msgstr "...Por eso lo mataron."

msgctxt "720_Tanimura"
msgid "Who was it, then!? Who murdered my dad!?\\r\n"
"And who finished the hit!?"
msgstr "¡¿Quién demonios es?! ¡¿Quién asesinó a mi padre?!\\r\n"
"¡¿Quién es el verdadero asesino?!"

msgctxt "732_Katsuragi"
msgid "Heh..."
msgstr "Je..."

msgctxt "756_Tanimura"
msgid "How long have you been here?"
msgstr "...¿Cuánto tiempo llevas aquí?"

msgctxt "768_Katsuragi"
msgid "Heh, since long before you arrived."
msgstr "Je... Estuve aquí mucho antes de que tú llegaras."

msgctxt "780_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "792_Katsuragi"
msgid "I'd wager you saw me in the crowd, but didn't recognize me."
msgstr "Es probable que me hayas visto en la multitud, pero no me reconociste."

msgctxt "804_Katsuragi"
msgid "That tells me you don't have much of a file on me. A relief, really."
msgstr "...Eso me dice que no has investigado mucho sobre mí. Eso me tranquiliza."

msgctxt "816_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "828_Katsuragi"
msgid "Now, what will it be? Shall we proceed with the deal?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿qué hacemos? ¿Seguiremos con el trato aquí?"

msgctxt "840_Tanimura"
msgid "No, let's walk and talk."
msgstr "No, ¿por qué no hablamos mientras caminamos un poco?"

msgctxt "852_Katsuragi"
msgid "Here?"
msgstr "¿Caminar, dices?"

msgctxt "864_Tanimura"
msgid "Around. Maybe it'll help jog your memory, y'know? I'm sure you have so much to tell."
msgstr "Sí. ¿Hablemos sobre la verdad de hace 25 años mientras damos un paseo?"

msgctxt "876_Katsuragi"
msgid "...You really have thought this through. A moving target is a lot harder to hit."
msgstr "Entiendo. Eres muy astuto... Si nos movemos mientras negociamos, será más difícil que nos localicen."

msgctxt "888_Tanimura"
msgid "Not to mention I thought you'd appreciate a nice, long stroll through Tojo Clan turf."
msgstr "¿No te gustaría caminar por el corazón del territorio del Clan Tojo?"

msgctxt "900_Katsuragi"
msgid "How thoughtful of you. Then lead the way, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "Qué considerado. Acepto acompañarle, Masayoshi Tanimura-san."

